catList: This objective of this course is to provide the basics of object-oriented software engineering including object-oriented analysis and design using UML. Course includes: Fundamental concepts of software design & UML (Unified Modeling Language), Requirement analysis, UML notations, Use case diagrams, Class diagrams and Case studies.
